    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you won't find another one like this\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition, inside and out. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions. I'm excited for it to go to a great new home!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
