    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for the serious collector is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 high-revving straight-six mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement to maintain chassis rigidity. The factory limited-slip differential provides optimal power delivery, while the suspension remains tight, preserving the razor-sharp turn-in and tactile feedback these chassis are renowned for. The exterior retains a deep, factory luster, and the interior bolsters show zero signs of fatigue. A true turn-key example for the purist seeking the zenith of naturally aspirated performance.",
